New features of UniConverter 14
Note: Upgrading may incur additional fees for users who are currently using the one-time purchase plan of Uniconverter.
1. Conversion and compression speed improved by 50%+.
2. MP4 and WEBM now support ALPHA transparent output.
3. Added support for lossless compression of audio files.
4. Compression quality improved by 80%, compressing to one-ninth of the original size without loss of quality.
5. Independent process for the media player, supporting decoding and playing of more than 1000 formats.
6. Exclusive support for special encoding such as AV1, HEVC,etc.
7. AI noise reduction, AI voice separation and AI voice change are now available for free for a limited time.
